# JHE Open Wearables polling cron — read by supercronic in the jhe_cron sidecar.
#
# The `ow_poll` management command no-ops automatically when `module.ow=false`
# in JheSettings, so this crontab can stay enabled even when the OW pipeline
# is disabled at the operator level.
#
# Default: poll every 15 minutes. Operators can adjust by editing this file
# and rebuilding the jhe_cron image.
*/15 * * * * cd /code && python manage.py ow_poll
